purchase_reason: I was drawn to this product because of its stylish design and versatility for various occasions. The lace trim and v-neck style appealed to my desire for something that could be both casual and elegant. I also appreciated the comfort of the fabric, which is important for my daily wear. However, I did have to consider the sizing, as I usually wear a smaller size but opted for a small, which turned out to be a bit big for me.

I chose this item primarily for its affordability and the assurance of quality that comes with the brand. The consistent sizing and the fact that it is designed to be long-lasting were significant factors in my decision. I was also influenced by the positive reviews that highlighted the softness and fit, which aligned with my needs for comfortable everyday clothing.
user_data.general_preference: I generally prefer high-quality, comfortable clothing that fits well and is versatile for various occasions. I value items that are made from breathable materials, have moisture-wicking properties, and offer a good fit, whether for casual wear or workouts. I appreciate products that come in a variety of colors and styles, allowing for personal expression. Additionally, I tend to favor items that are durable and maintain their quality after multiple washes. On the other hand, I dislike products that are poorly made, do not fit as expected, or arrive late. I also find it unappealing when clothing lacks comfort or is not suitable for everyday use.
